About 200 from Aba Golf Club, Benin Golf Club, Python and Port Harcourt Golf Club, and other golf clubs nationwide will converge at the Ibori Golf and Country Club (IGCC) to usher in Queen Mowah as the 12th Lady Captain of the club. The tournament holds between June 17th and 18th 2021.   Ronaldo out of Portugal squad for Switzerland game     Aston Villa make Oxlade-Chamberlain ‘top priority’     Etim Esin wants help over lingering knee problem   The former lady captain of Ibadan Golf Club and Tiger Golf Club Sumbo Oshile described Queen Mowah as ‘a lady captain with a big heart,’ thereby assuring participants of a well-packaged event. “Queen Mowah is evidently a seasoned organizer who is a confident golfer,”